0Style%2C%20Substance%2C%20Spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20vibrant%20colour%20palette%2C%20an%20array%20of%20wonderful%20musical%20tracks%2C%20the%20infectious%20verve%20of%20young%20actors%2C%20and%20a%20period%20story%20imbued%20with%20concerns%20of%20contemporary%20relevance%20propel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fagastya-nanda-makes-a-hilarious-confession-about-his-social-media-absence-4641600%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20zone%20where%20even%20the%20palpably%20facile%20is%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20fun%20and%20marked%20by%20stylistic%20flair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20live-action%20musical%20coming-of-age%20comedy%20transplants%20the%20abiding%20Archie%20comics%20to%20a%20mid-1960s%20Anglo-Indian%20hill%20town%20setting.%20It%20conjures%20up%20a%20largely%20believable%20universe%20within%20a%20bubble%20of%20mirth%20and%20music%20in%20which%20a%20group%20of%20thick-as-thieves%20high%20schoolers%20navigate%20love%2C%20friendship%20and%20heartbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20are%20at%20it%2C%20the%20free-spirited%20youngsters%20also%20learn%20that%20there%20is%20much%20more%20to%20life%20than%20dates%20and%20parties%2C%20banter%20and%20bonhomie%20and%20figure%20out%20that%20one%20is%20never%20too%20young%20to%20spark%20a%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPat%20and%20predictable%20as%20that%20may%20be%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khan-on-daughter-suhanas-debut-in-the-archies-lovely-to-see-your-children-starting-to-work-hard-4640027%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20an%20easy-flowing%20rhythm%20thanks%20to%20a%20gallery%20of%20vivid%20characters%20that%20are%20never%20archetypal%20even%20though%20they%20possess%20clear-cut%20characteristics.%20The%20film%20flows%20without%20a%20hitch%20and%20articulates%20its%20points%20with%20a%20refreshing%20lightness%20of%20touch%20while%20literally%20making%20a%20song%20and%20dance%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchie%20Andrews%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Famitabh-abhishek-bachchan-aishwarya-rai-bachchan-with-daughter-aaradhya-at-the-archies-screening-4637072%5C%22%3EAgastya%20Nanda%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20in%20a%20dilemma%20of%20his%20own%20making.%20He%20is%20caught%20between%20the%20vivacious%20Veronica%20Lodge%20(Suhana%20Khan)%2C%20who%20has%20just%20returned%20to%20Riverdale%20after%20being%20away%20from%20her%20hometown%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20the%20sedate%20Betty%20Cooper%20(Khushi%20Kapoor).%20He%20has%20feelings%20for%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchie%2C%20son%20of%20the%20owner%20of%20Riverdale's%20only%20travel%20agency%2C%20has%20such%20faith%20in%20his%20own%20aura%20that%20he%20presumes%20that%20neither%20of%20the%20two%20girls%20will%20have%20any%20problem%20with%20his%20habitual%20two-timing.%20This%20may%20be%201964%20but%20Veronica%20and%20Betty%20are%20'modern'%20and%20tough%20young%20women%20who%20value%20their%20friendship%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20knows%20when%20and%20how%20to%20assert%20their%20agency%20despite%20their%20hearts%20being%20expectedly%20prone%20to%20possessiveness%2C%20envy%20and%20sorrow.%20Their%20strong%20bonding%20faces%20its%20share%20of%20up%20and%20downs.%20How%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20reverses%20forms%20an%20important%20part%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20girl%20in%20their%20gang%2C%20Ethel%20Muggs%20(Dot.)%2C%20is%20the%20very%20best%20at%20what%20she%20does%20-%20she%20is%20a%20much%20sought-after%20hairstylist.%20Her%20allegiance%20to%20her%20employer%2C%20Pam%20(Delnaaz%20Irani)%2C%20is%20tested%20when%20a%20new%20salon%20with%20imported%2C%20state-of-the-art%20equipment%20opens%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20for%20a%20moment%20do%20the%20three%20leads%20seem%20to%20be%20raw%20as%20actors.%20They%20deliver%20the%20goods%20with%20remarkable%20elan.%20No%20less%20impressive%20are%20the%20actors%20who%20complete%20the%20young%20cast%20that%20fleshes%20out%20Archie%20Comics%20characters%20with%20distinct%20individual%20traits%20without%20letting%20any%20of%20them%20sink%20into%20predictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVedang%20Raina%20as%20Reggie%20Mantle%2C%20Mihir%20Ahuja%20as%20Jughead%20and%20Yuvraj%20Menda%20as%20the%20nerdy%2C%20self-effacing%20Dilton%20Doiley%20(who%20proves%20his%20worth%20when%20it%20really%20matters)%20sail%20through%20their%20roles%20with%20utmost%20ease.%20The%20script%20is%20their%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20mixes%20spoken%20dialogues%20with%20a%20slew%20of%20songs%20that%20provide%20clear%20glimpses%20into%20volatile%20minds%20as%20the%20bubbly%20teenagers%20make%20their%20ways%20through%20a%20crucial%20phase%20of%20their%20lives%20that%20sees%20them%20transition%20to%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20the%20characters%20and%20their%20city%20remain%20unchanged%20in%20The%20Archies%20but%20everything%20else%20in%20the%20Netflix%20film%20directed%20by%20Zoya%20Akhtar%20and%20written%20by%20her%20with%20Reema%20Kagti%20and%20Ayesha%20DeVitre%20Dhillon%20is%20given%20lively%20new%20trappings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20glaring%20disconnect%20between%20what%20the%20comics%20are%20-%20an%20American%20pop%20culture%20phenomenon%20(that%20had%20huge%20currency%20on%20the%20subcontinent%20especially%20in%20the%201960s%20and%201970s)%20-%20and%20the%20delightfully%20cheerful%20fable%20about%20a%20community%20with%20deep%20roots%20in%20India's%20colonial%20past%20and%20yet%20wholly%20committed%2C%20post-Independence%2C%20to%20the%20land%20of%20their%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freshness%20of%20the%20brew%20that%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%20rustles%20up%20rests%20primarily%20on%20the%20flamboyant%20and%20fastidious%20visual%20design%20and%20the%20flourish%20that%20the%20principal%20actors%20impart%20to%20the%20film%2C%20which%20addresses%20the%20pangs%20of%20growing%20up%20and%20standing%20up%20for%20a%20cause%20while%20it%20tackles%20the%20larger%20themes%20of%20corporate%20greed%2C%20media%20freedom%20and%20the%20scourge%20of%20unsustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20striking%20aspect%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20blends%20the%20flip%20(not%20flimsy)%20with%20the%20solemn%20(not%20self-conscious)%20as%20a%20group%20of%20teenagers%20deal%20with%20each%20other's%20angularities%2C%20their%20parents'%20desires%2C%20and%20the%20impositions%20of%20powerful%20people%20bent%20upon%20robbing%20their%20city%20of%20something%20its%20denizens%20hold%20dear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20celebrates%20the%20restless%2C%20kinetic%20spirit%20of%20the%20young%20even%20as%20it%20skewers%20the%20skullduggery%20that%20is%20afoot%20in%20the%20name%20of%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20town%20square%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20shopping%20plaza%20and%20a%20grand%20hotel%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20Riverdale's%20tourism%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20council%20head%20Dawson%20(Vinay%20Pathak)%20is%20in%20cahoots%20with%20entrepreneur%20Hiram%20Lodge%20(Ally%20Khan)%2C%20Veronica's%20ever-busy%2C%20profit-obsessed%20father.%20The%20two%20men%20manipulate%20the%20council%20members%20to%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20Green%20Park%2C%20a%20space%20where%20the%20city's%20roots%20literally%20lie%2C%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20construction%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20just%20live%20your%20life%20for%20kicks%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Riverdale%20High%20students%20croon%20when%20Archie%20says%20he%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20politics.%20He%20plans%20to%20fly%20away%20to%20London%20to%20study%20even%20though%20his%20parents%20aren't%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20idea.%20Betty%2C%20Reggie%2C%20Jughead%2C%20Ethel%20and%20Dilton%20have%20no%20such%20escape%20route.%20They%20have%20far%20too%20m