Independence%20and%20the%20death%20of%20its%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20-%20neither%20of%20the%20two%20signposts%20of%20Indian%20history%20is%20specifically%20mentioned%20-%20were%20separated%20by%2017%20years.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20age%20of%20the%20younger%20characters%20in%20the%20film.%20They%20are%20as%20old%20as%20the%20free%20nation%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20indeed%20politics.%20Even%20when%20life%20is%20awash%20with%20colours%2C%20songs%2C%20dances%20and%20the%20elixir%20of%20youth%20the%20way%20it%20is%20in%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E.%20A%20beguiling%20oddity.%20In%20style%2C%20substance%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701939960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Flthecqig_the-archies_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-archies-review-a-beguiling-oddity-in-style-substance-and-spirit-3-stars-4641888%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Archies%20Review%3A%20Not%20for%20a%20moment%20do%20the%20three%20leads%20seem%20to%20be%20raw%20as%20actors.%20They%20deliver%20the%20goods%20with%20remarkable%20elan.%20No%20less%20impressive%20are%20the%20actors%20who%20complete%20the%20young%20cast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-archies-review-a-beguiling-oddity-in-style-substance-and-spirit-3-stars-4641888%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netherlands%20Oscar%20Contender%20%E2%80%98Sweet%20Dreams%E2%80%99%20Sets%20North%20American%20Release%20With%20Dekanalog%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701939660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FSweet-Dreams.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235825435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ena%20Sendijarevi%C4%87%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CSweet%20Dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20Netherlands%E2%80%99%20submission%20in%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20international%20feature%20category%2C%20has%20secured%20North%20American%20distribution%20via%20Dekanalog.%20The%20film%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20Locarno%2C%20where%20it%20won%20the%20Pardo%20for%20best%20performance%20for%20Ren%C3%A9e%20Soutendijk%20(%E2%80%9CSuspiria%E2%80%9D)%20and%20the%20second%20prize%20of%20the%20junior%20jury.%20The%20film%20debuted%20in%20North%20America%20in%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnetherlands-oscar-sweet-dreams-north-american-release-dekanalog-1235825435%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnetherlands-oscar-sweet-dreams-north-american-release-dekanalog-1235825435%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnetherlands-oscar-sweet-dreams-north-american-release-dekanalog-1235825435%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20GDP%20Growth%20Figures%20Reflect%20Robustness%20or%20a%20Statistical%20Overstatement%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18150619%2FDown-graph-p.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20razzmatazz%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Fgdp-surges-76-per-cent-in-2023-july-to-september-quarter-goes-past-rbi-forecast%2Farticle67591434.ece%5C%22%3Erobust%207.6%25%20real%20second%20quarter%20(Q2)%20GDP%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20pumped%20up%20an%20adrenaline%20rush%20last%20week%2C%20prompting%20many%20to%20up%20their%20projections%20for%20fiscal%20year%202024%20(FY24)%20closer%20to%207%25%2C%20higher%20than%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20projection%20of%206.5%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20is%20obscured%20is%20that%20consumer%20companies%20are%20facing%20a%20supply%20gridlock%20as%20demand%20falls%2C%20inventories%20pile%20up%2C%20and%20the%20festive%20season%20demand%20remained%20weak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeparately%2C%20there%20is%20extensive%20evidence%20of%20flatness%20in%20real%20incomes%20of%20households%20(76%25%20of%20the%20GDP)%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20data%20on%20the%20contraction%20of%20financial%20savings%20and%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20report.%20CMIE%20says%20that%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20spiked%20again%2C%20to%20an%20average%20of%209.5%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20there%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20stupendous%20GDP%20data%20and%20the%20lugubrious%20household%20situation%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20think%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%20lies%20in%20the%20way%20GDP%20is%20calculated%2C%20which%20is%20confounded%20with%20systemic%20statistical%20aberrations.%20While%20the%20headline%20real%20GDP%20growth%20numbers%20are%20disconnected%20from%20the%20ground%20reality%2C%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20discrepancies%20shows%20the%20true%20picture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20robust%20headline%20growth%20situation%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%207.4%25%20year-on-year%20(YoY)%20gross%20value%20added%20(GVA)%20growth%2C%20employment-intensive%20agriculture%20and%20services%20%E2%80%93%20which%20together%20contribute%2072%25%20of%20the%20GVA%20%E2%80%93%20saw%20a%20major%20deceleration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERobust%20contribution%20from%20manufacturing%20and%20construction%2C%20which%20grew%20by%2013.9%25%20and%2013.3%25%20YoY%20respectively%2C%20translating%20into%20Industry%20GVA%20growth%20of%2013.2%25%2C%20essentially%20derives%20from%20the%20imputed%20higher%20value%20addition.%20This%20was%20due%20to%20low%20inflation%20related%20to%20the%20WPI%20driving%20up%20margins%20and%20profits%20of%20large%20firms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20expenditure%20side%2C%20real%20GDP%20growth%20at%207.6%25%2C%20however%2C%20encloses%20weak%20core%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPutting%20the%20identified%20components%20of%20the%20expenditure%20GDP%20explained%20by%20the%20components%20of%20household%20and%20government%20consumption%2C%20capital%20formation%2C%20and%20net%20exports%2C%20i.e.%20GDP%20excluding%20the%20unexplained%20discrepancy%20portion%2C%20the%20real%20core%20GDP%20stands%20at%203.0%25%20in%20Q2%20of%20FY24%2C%20following%201.4%25%20in%20Q1.%20This%20is%20only%2040%25%20of%20the%20reported%20GDP%20of%207.6%25%20in%20Q2!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20contrastingly%20frail%20household%20income%20situation%20(a%20la%20PLFS%202022-23%2C%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20savings%20data%20FY23)%2C%20the%20continued%20slackness%20in%20private%20capex%20and%20deceleration%20in%20trade%2C%20the%20divergent%20core%20(2.3%25%20YoY%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY24)%20and%20headline%20real%20GDP%20growth%20(7.7%25)%20are%20not%20trivial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20substantial%2071%25%20unexplained%20portion%20of%20the%20real%20GDP%20growth%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY24%20is%20because%20the%20estimated%20real%20GVA%20side%2C%20representing%20the%20value%20added%20from%20production%20across%20all%20sectors%2C%20is%202.7%25%20higher%20than%20the%20real%20core%20expenditure%20GDP.%20But%20for%20the%20discrepancies%2C%20the%20real%20GVA%20plus%20net%20indirect%20taxes%20should%20match%20with%20the%20real%20GDP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20discrepancy%20is%20cause%20for%20worry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENormally%2C%20discrepancies%20should%20not%20be%20worrisome%20if%20it%20is%20a%20random%20error%2C%20where%20frequent%20offsetting%20positive%20and%20negative%20deviations%20average%20at%20zero.%20But%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20average%20discrepancy%20during%20Q1%20FY12%20to%20Q2%20FY24%20is%20%2B0.6%25%20of%20GDP%20with%20a%20maximum%20of%205.4%25%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20-3.9%25%3B%2032%20out%20of%2050%20quarters%20saw%20a%20positive%20discrepancy%2C%20indicating%20that%20real%20GVA%20exceeded%20core%20GDP%20in%2064%25%20of%20quarters.%20And%20more%20importantly%2C%20it%20has%20an%20inverse%20correlation%20of%20(-)0.63%20with%20the%20GDP%2FGVA%20deflator%2C%20which%20rose%20to%20(-)0.76%20in%20the%20post-pandemic%20era.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20overestimation%20of%20GVA%20occurred%20during%20times%20of%20falling%20inflation%20or%20deflation%2C%20mainly%20driven%20by%20WPI.%20Thus%2C%20indexed%20to%20Q2%20FY12%2C%20the%20real%20GDP%20in%20Q2%20FY24%20is%203.8%25%20(or%20Rs%201.6%20trillion)%20higher%20than%20the%20core%20real%20GDP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20discrepancies%20capturing%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20unaccounted%20GDP%20growth%20are%20not%20random%20and%20relate%20to%20the%20usage%20of%20WPI%20as%20a%20deflator%20to%20derive%20real%20GVA.%20Such%20systemic%20discrepancies%2C%20therefore%2C%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20real%20GDP%20estimation%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGVA%20is%20the%20value%20of%20output%20excluding%20net%20indirect%20tax%20less%20cost%20of%20input%20consumption%20valued%20at%20purchasers%E2%80%99%20prices.%20Hence%2C%20the%20measured%20value%20added%20would%20rise%20sharply%20with%20a%20fall%20in%20commodity%20or%20raw%20material%20prices%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20recently%2C%20even%20with%20slowing%20consumption%20demand%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20scenario%20where%20large%20firms%20have%20gained%20considerable%20operating%20margins%20due%20to%20elevated%20monopolistic%20power%20since%20mid-2016%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20smaller%20firms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConversely%2C%20given%20the%20sharp%20deceleration%20in%20estimated%20household%20real%20disposable%20incomes%20to%202%25%20YoY%20in%20FY23%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20jobs%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20decline%20in%20savings%20and%20slowing%20consumption%20and%20flat%20real%20wage%20earnings%20in%20four%20years%20(PLFS%202022-23)%2C%20the%20real%20core%20GDP%20growth%20or%20the%20demand%20side%20does%20not%20share%20the%20robustness%20of%20the%20output%20side%20or%20estimated%20GVA%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20PLFS%20data%20also%20indicating%20a%20structural%20rise%20in%20dependence%20of%20households%20on%20less%20productive%20rural%20(73.3%25%20of%20the%20population)%20and%20agri%20(45.8%25%20of%20workers%2C%202022-23)%2C%20the%20resultant%20decline%20in%20labour%20productivity%20and%20the%20household%20income%20which%20contributes%2076%25%20of%20GDP%20is%20misaligned%20with%20the%20sharp%20gains%20in%20reported%20productivity%20of%20the%20producing%20firms%20represented%20by%20real%20GVA%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20feebleness%20of%20the%20household%20consumption%20demand%20combined%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20private%20investment%20and%20the%20recent%20deceleration%20in%20exports%20has%20overpowered%20robust%20government%20capex.%20Hence%2C%20the%20aggregate%20demand%20remains%20significantly%20weak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fkaran-thapar-pronab-sen-gdp-data-transcript%5C%22%3EFull%20Text%3A%20Pronab%20Sen%20Explains%20Why%20Data%20on%20Which%20GDP%20Is%20Calculated%20Is%20A%20Major%20Concern%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20crucial%20factor%20is%20that%20the%20deflator%20used%20for%20deriving%20the%20real%20GVA%20is%20highly%20correlated%20with%20the%20WPI%20inflation.%20However%2C%20given%20the%20dominant%20contribution%20of%20household%20consumption%2C%20core%20expenditure%20GDP%20is%20also%20sensitive%20to%20CPI%20inflation.%20Hence%2C%20the%20sharp%20decline%20in%20WPI%20inflation%20(-1.8%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY24)%20and%20higher%20CPI%20inflation%20(5.5%25)%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20divergence%20between%20low%20real%20core%20GDP%20and%20strong%20GVA%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20all%20put%20together%2C%20the%20GVA%20side%20of%20the%20national%20income%20is%20susceptible%20to%20over-identification%20of%20large%20surviving%20companies%20that%20have%20gained%20market%20share%20from%20the%20non-corporate%20smaller%20firms%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20and%20services%20industries.%20As%20a%20corollary%2C%20it%20underrepresents%20the%20falling%20productivity%20arising%20from%20gaining%20ruralisation.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20also%20susceptible%20to%20higher%20projections%20of%20gross%20value%20added%20due%20to%20the%20sharp%20decline%20in%20commodity%20prices%20(or%20underestimation%20in%20times%20of%20sharp%20rise%20in%20commodity%20prices).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrastingly%2C%20growth%20in%20real%20GDP%20ex%20discrepancies%20is%20a%20more%20relatable%20measure%20to%20depict%20the%20actual%20situation%20of%20the%20households%E2%80%99%20livelihood%2C%20employment%20and%20productivity.%20Also%2C%20unlike%20the%20GVA%20estimates%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20exclusion%20and%20volatility%20induced%20by%20WPI%20inflation%20is%20much%20lesser%20in%20real%20core%20GDP.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20the%20endogenous%20growth%2C%20depicting%20the%20situation%20of%20households%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20income%20and%20consumption%20capability%20remains%20very%20weak.%20Behind%20the%20robust%20real%20headline%20GDP%20growth%2C%20padded%20up%20by%20overstated%20GVA%20is%20a%20flattening%20trend%20in%20the%20core%20real%20GDP%20growth%2C%20which%20is%20worrisome.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%20the%20enfeebled%20demand%20reflects%20the%20structural%20issues%2C%20as%20the%20divergence%20between%20CPI%20and%20WPI%20inflation%20eventually%20narrows%20it%20would%20imply%20that%20the%20reported%20GDP%20will%20also%20converge%20towards%20the%20lower%20structural%20trend%20in%20core%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fdhananjay-sinha%5C%22%3EDhananjay%20Sinha%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20co-head%20of%20Equities%20and%20head%20of%20Research%20of%20Strategy%20and%20Economics%20at%20Systematix%20Group.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701939655000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18150619%2FDown-graph-p.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-growth-figures-robustness-or-statistical-overstatement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20the%20contrastingly%20frail%20household%20income%20situation%2C%20the%20continued%20slackness%20in%20private%20capex%20and%20deceleration%20in%20trade%2C%20the%20divergent%20core%20and%20headline%20real%20GDP%20growth%20are%20not%20trivial.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-growth-figures-robustness-or-statistical-overstatement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Republican%20debate%20turns%20personal%20with%20harsh%20attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701939456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105808553%2Cimgsize-63302.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frepublican-debate-turns-personal-with-harsh-attacks%2Farticleshow%2F105808480.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frepublican-debate-turns-personal-with-harsh-attacks%2Farticleshow%2F105808480.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Despite%20Higher%20Overall%20Vote%2C%20Congress%20Loses%20Three%20Hindi%20Belt%20States%3A%20What's%20The%20Way%20Forward%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F08195755%2FFvdM0YTWwAASRHL.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20odd%20months%20before%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%20due%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20lost%20three%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20contest%20was%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20said%20three%20states%20and%20not%20between%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20already%20media%20channels%20friendly%20to%20powers-that-be%20are%20busy%20touting%20this%20Congress%20loss%20as%20that%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20Congress%20pulled%20off%20victories%20that%20many%20pollsters%20had%20envisioned%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20most%20primetime%20debates%20(sic)%20would%20have%20been%20to%20say%20that%20assembly%20elections%20after%20all%20remain%20unrelated%20to%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20psyche.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20lost%2C%20the%20assembly%20results%20are%20sought%20to%20be%20extrapolated%20to%20endorse%20the%20Modi%20slogan%20that%20the%20three-state%20victory%20of%20the%20BJP%20foreshadows%20a%20coming%20%E2%80%9Chattrick%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20to%20note%20in%20passing%3A%20the%20Congress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3Epolled%3C%2Fa%3E%204%20crore%2090%20lakh%20votes%20in%20the%20five%20states%20that%20went%20to%20polls%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tally%20of%204%20crore%2081%20lakh%20popular%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tally%20of%20popular%20support%20may%20discourage%20the%20view%20that%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20is%2C%20as%20the%20right-wing%20likes%20to%20propagate%2C%20a%20miserable%20political%20has-been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20another%20matter%2C%20though%2C%20that%20in%20our%20flawed%20version%20of%20representative%20democracy%2C%20votes%20polled%20do%20not%20necessarily%20match%20in%20a%20rational%20way%20the%20seats%20won%20by%20a%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20corporates%20whom%20a%20two-party%20system%20suits%20best%2C%20where%20each%20party%20is%2C%20at%20bottom%2C%C2%A0%20in%20terms%20of%20class%20interest%2C%20a%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20other%2C%20have%20used%20their%20clout%20to%20defeat%20any%20attempt%20to%20install%20a%20system%20of%20proportional%20representation%2C%20wherein%20all%20political%20contestants%20are%20rewarded%20with%20seats%20proportionate%20to%20the%20votes%20polled%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%20stands%20to%20redefine%20the%20power%20equations%20between%20it%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20may%20make%20entrenched%20regional%20forces%20particularly%20wary%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20succeeded%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-small-coterie-hubris-and-forgetting-that-the-era-of-doras-is-over-what-hurt-kcr%5C%22%3Evanquishing%20a%20powerful%20regional%20satrap%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Telangana%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20history%20that%20a%20national%20party%20has%20done%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidence%20of%20this%20new%20equilibrium%20between%20a%20chastened%20Congress%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20came%20when%20four%20stalwart%20leaders%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%20stated%20their%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20alliance%20called%20by%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%20December%206%2C%20causing%20the%20said%20meeting%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fopposition-india-bloc-meeting-slated-to-be-held-tomorrow-postponed-after-top-leaders-decide-to-skip-2472148-2023-12-05%5C%22%3Ecancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20replaced%20by%20one%20in%20which%20parliamentary%20floor%20leaders%20participated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20there%20is%20outspoken%20criticism%20from%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20that%20the%20ambition%20of%20the%20Congress%20to%20try%20its%20muscle%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own%20resulted%20in%20the%20sidelining%20of%20the%20man%20who%20has%20been%20the%20brain%20behind%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20all-party%20joint%20challenge%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20namely%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20have%20been%20thought%20with%20justice%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20projected%20as%20the%20vanguard%20leader%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20order%20to%20enable%20a%20sharp%20focus%20on%20its%20ideological%20initiative%20related%20to%20seeking%20justice%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20the%20credit%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20party%20that%20they%20successfully%20persuaded%20ambitious%20regional%20forces%2C%20often%20antagonistic%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20that%20no%20alliance%20without%20the%20Congress%20would%20have%20the%20least%20chance%20of%20ousting%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20need%20not%20be%20abject%20after%20the%20assembly%20losses%2C%20given%20its%20tally%20of%20the%20popular%20vote%3B%20but%20when%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20assessing%20prospects%20of%20various%20member%20parties%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20regard%20to%20each%20single%20parliamentary%20constituency%20begins%20within%20the%20alliance%2C%20hopefully%20without%20loss%20of%20time%2C%20the%20Congress%20must%20be%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20support%20the%20candidature%20of%20member%20parties%20in%20constituencies%20where%20they%20provenly%20deserve%20to%20be%20protagonists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20in%20the%20two%20hundred%20or%20so%20parliamentary%20segments%20where%20the%20Congress%20remains%20the%20chief%20antagonist%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20all%20others%20must%20be%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20contribute%20what%20clout%20they%20can%20muster%20so%20that%20the%20fatally%20crucial%20electoral%20strategy%20of%20one-on-one%20contests%20is%20not%20derailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20state%20like%20Kerala%2C%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20an%20even%20distribution%20of%20seats%20may%20be%20advisable%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20assembly%20gains%20in%20the%20just%20concluded%20elections%20promise%20little%20to%20the%20BJP%20centrally%2C%20given%20that%20they%20already%20have%20some%2061%20parliamentary%20seats%20from%20a%20total%20of%2065%20in%20the%20three%20Hindi-belt%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one-on-one%20contests%20do%20materialise%2C%20that%20tally%20is%20only%20likely%20to%20dwindle%20in%20these%20states%20rather%20than%20increase%2C%20as%20in%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right-wing%20hype%20thus%20needs%20to%20be%20isolated%20from%20the%20actual%20prospects%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nitty%20gritty%20lies%20in%20this%3A%20the%20point-counterpoint%20among%20the%20alliance%20partners%20must%20cease%20forthwith%2C%20and%20the%20business%20of%20putting%20heads%20together%20to%20formulate%20both%20a%20common%20agenda%20and%20an%20agreed%20seat-sharing%20format%20be%20accomplished%20and%20made%20known%20with%20dispatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20of%20course%20will%20happen%20only%20if%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20Congress%20included%2C%20acknowledges%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20existential%20moment%20in%20our%20post-Independence%20history%3A%20should%20the%20Modi-led%20right-wing%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024%2C%20the%20constitutional%20order%20may%20come%20to%20be%20%3Ci%3Eformally%3C%2Fi%3E%20jettisoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20unless%20all%20partners%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20persuade%20themselves%20to%20believe%20the%20truth%20of%20that%20likelihood%20will%20the%20alliance%20fructify%20as%20a%20force%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20the%20voter%20be%20persuaded%20of%20both%20the%20sincerity%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20the%20actuality%20of%20the%20prospect%20that%20confronts%20the%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20take%20some%20doing%3A%20it%20will%20be%20no%20easy%20task%20to%20counter%20and%20neutralize%20the%20propaganda%20blitz%20that%20the%20ruling%20right%20wing%20will%20unleash%20with%20the%20full%20endorsement%20of%20media%20channels%20and%20money%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20best%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20now%20a%20cult%20figure%20for%20some%2036%25%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20see%20him%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdefender%20of%20the%20faith%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20are%20quite%20willing%20to%20place%20%3Ci%3ESanatan%20%3C%2Fi%3Eabove%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20law%2C%20much%20as%20Salafi%2F%20Wahabi%20Muslims%20place%20the%20%3Ci%3ESharia%3C%2Fi%3E%20above%20the%20democratic%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20to%20remind%20ourselves%3A%20when%20L.K.%20Advani%20set%20out%20on%20his%20most%20consequential%20%3Ci%3Erath%20yatra%20%3C%2Fi%3Ein%201990%2C%20it%20was%20his%20objective%20to%20transform%20Hinduism%20into%20an%20Abrahamic%20construct%3B%20the%20new%20Hindu%20order%20was%20to%20have%20but%20one%20God%20in%20Ram%2C%20one%20chief%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20and%20but%20one%20scripture%2C%20namely%20the%20%3Ci%3ERamcharitmanas.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20%3Ci%3Eputsch%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20meant%20to%20negate%20the%20ground%20reality%20that%20Hindus%20were%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20indubitably%20divided%20among%20social%20groups%20whose%20conjoint%20interests%20and%20loyalties%20often%20vitiated%20any%20monochromatic%20communal%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20remain%20a%20curiosity%20of%20a%20high%20order%20whether%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20Advani%20had%20become%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20that%20which%20Ambedkar%20had%20cautioned%20the%20republic-to-be%20about%20has%20come%20to%20pass%3A%20%3Ci%3Ebhakti%20%3C%2Fi%3E(unquestioning%20devotion)%3Ci%3E%20%3C%2Fi%3Ehas%20indeed%20overtaken%20political%20life%20in%20India%2C%20and%2C%20the%20dominant%20trope%20of%20public%2Fpolitical%20life%20has%20come%20to%20be%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20thus%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%3B%20if%20it%20fails%20the%20call%20of%20history%2C%20the%20Indian%20Republic%20may%20decisively%20go%20the%20way%20of%20Weimar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2060%25%20of%20India%20stands%20either%20to%20sink%20or%20swim%20together%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20must%20refrain%20from%20being%20carried%20away%20by%20its%20most%20heartening%20revival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20many%20other%20constituents%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20must%20also%20rise%20both%20above%20pique%20and%20solipsistic%20opportunism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lesson%20that%20the%20political%20life%20of%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20brought%20home%20is%20that%20democracy%20is%20still%20not%20a%20non-negotiable%20principle%2C%20even%20for%20the%20very%20highly%20educated%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20cloutless%20%3Ci%3Ehoi%20polloi%3C%2Fi%3E%20sta