karjun%20Kharge%2C%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20congratulated%20Mr%20Reddy%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20assuring%20his%20full%20support%20to%20Telangana's%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECongratulations%20to%20Shri%20Revanth%20Reddy%20Garu%20on%20taking%20oath%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Telangana.%20I%20assure%20all%20possible%20support%20to%20further%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20citizens.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frevanth_anumula%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40revanth_anumula%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1732674215856447893%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20office%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20and%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20held%20a%20victory%20lap%20inside%20the%20stadium%20in%20an%20open%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20trounced%20the%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao-led%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20ruling%20Telangana%20since%20its%20formation%20in%202014%2C%20by%20winning%2065%20out%20of%20119%20Assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20Tiger%20Revanth%20by%20his%20supporters%2C%20has%20been%20credited%20to%20have%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20Congress's%20victory.%20A%20former%20TDP%20leader%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20switched%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%202017.%20He%20was%20appointed%20Telangana%20Congress%20president%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20led%20a%20spirited%20campaign%20against%20the%20KCR-led%20government%20and%20was%20seen%20leading%20street%20protests%20and%20public%20demonstrations%20over%20a%20host%20of%20issues.%20The%20Congress's%20efforts%20bore%20fruit%20and%20the%20party%20trumped%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20however%2C%20had%20a%20challenge%20waiting%20for%20him.%20Soon%20after%20the%20victory%2C%20his%20detractors%20within%20the%20party%20opposed%20his%20elevation%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20They%20pointed%20to%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20him%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20money%20in%20exchange%20for%20poll%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20had%20fought%20hard%20to%20get%20his%20loyalists%20tickets%2C%20knowing%20well%20that%20he%20would%20not%20get%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20if%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20support%20of%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20MLAs.%20This%20worked%20well%20for%20him%20and%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20upset%20the%20apple%20cart%2C%20endorsed%20Mr%20Reddy's%20claim%20to%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20faces%20the%20tall%20challenge%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20Congress's%20poll%20guarantees%20and%20preparing%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20due%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701937320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foohhrj7o_revanth-reddy_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-gandhis-attend-swearing-in-ceremony-4641721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anumula%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20chief%20of%20Telangana%20Congress%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20party's%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20November%2030%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20was%20today%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20state's%20second%20Chief%20Minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-a