ala%20Sitharaman%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20today%20said%20the%20budget%20to%20be%20presented%20on%20February%201%2C%202024%20would%20not%20have%20any%20%26quot%3Bspectacular%20announcement%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20would%20be%20a%20vote%20on%20account%20in%20run%20up%20to%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20truth%20that%20February%201%2C%202024%20budget%20that%20will%20be%20announced%20will%20just%20be%20a%20vote%20on%20account%20because%20we%20will%20be%20in%20an%20election%20mode.%20So%20the%20budget%20that%20the%20government%20presents%20will%20just%20be%20to%20meet%20the%20expenditure%20of%20the%20government%20till%20a%20new%20government%20comes%20to%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20CII%20Global%20Economic%20Policy%20Forum%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20country%20would%20be%20preparing%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20which%20are%20due%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20February%201%20budget%2C%20following%20the%20British%20tradition%2C%20is%20called%20vote%20on%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20spectacular%20announcements%20come%20in%20that%20time%20(in%20vote%20on%20account).%20So%20you%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20till%20after%20new%20government%20comes%20in%20and%20presents%20next%20full%20Budget%20in%20July%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%201%2C%202024%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20will%20present%20an%20interim%20budget%20for%202024-25%20fiscal%2C%20beginning%20April%201%2C%202024%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20budget%20which%20is%20also%20known%20an%20a%20vote%20on%20account%20will%20allow%20the%20incumbent%20government%20to%20undertake%20expenditures%20till%20a%20new%20government%20is%20formed%20after%20general%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20t