bu%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Fmy-life-with-the-walter-boys-review-netflix-1235815349%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Fmy-life-with-the-walter-boys-review-netflix-1235815349%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Fmy-life-with-the-walter-boys-review-netflix-1235815349%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Witnessing%20Palestine%20in%20New%20York%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Watching%20India's%20Moral%20Vision%20Disappear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20to%20New%20York%20as%20a%20graduate%20student%20three%20years%20ago.%20These%20three%20years%20have%20been%20the%20most%20demanding%20and%20stimulating%20period%20of%20my%20academic%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20and%20joyous%20accidents%20of%20this%20journey%20has%20been%20my%20close%20friendship%20with%20fellow%20Arab%20students%20in%20this%20city.%20I%20have%20shared%20a%20house%20with%20a%20Syrian%20and%20a%20Palestinian%20here%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20have%20grown%20to%20call%20it%20a%20home.%20I%20now%20make%20makloubeh%20with%20lal%20mirch%20and%20garam%20masala.%20Pita%20bread%20with%20zaatar%20and%20olive%20oil%20has%20become%20my%20go-to%20midnight%20snack.%20I%20have%20gotten%20drunk%20on%20arak%20and%20unsuccessfully%20danced%20dabke%20at%20parties.%20The%20Delhi%20boy%20in%20me%20has%20also%20learned%20to%20cuss%20in%20Arabic%20now.%20These%20friendships%20have%20made%20me%20realise%20how%20similar%20we%20are%20to%20each%20other%20as%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20in%20the%20city%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20Palestinian%20Christian%20whose%20family%20was%20displaced%20from%20Jerusalem%20in%201948%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20exile%20ever%20since.%20My%20roommate%20is%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20family%20have%20to%20face%20the%20everyday%20humiliation%20of%20crossing%20Israeli%20checkpoints%20to%20travel%20in%20their%20own%20country.%20It%20did%20not%20start%20on%20October%207%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20hearing%20stories%20about%20the%20Israeli%20settler%20violence%20in%20occupied%20Palestine%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20I%20know%20people%20in%20this%20city%20whose%20houses%20have%20been%20bombed%2C%20and%20whose%20family%20members%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20arbitrarily%20arrested%2C%20and%20displaced%20in%20Palestine.%20I%20attach%20human%20faces%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Ramallah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20will%20not%20pretend%20to%20write%20from%20a%20neutral%20and%20distanced%20position%20today.%20Neutrality%20often%20helps%20the%20oppressor%2C%20not%20the%20oppressed.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Palestine%20has%20become%20as%20far%20and%20as%20close%20as%20India%2C%20in%20some%20ways.%20When%20I%20read%20the%20news%20from%20Gaza%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20hits%20me%20as%20if%20something%20horrible%20is%20unfolding%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20destruction%20of%20Gaza%20has%20shaken%20the%20world%20to%20the%20core.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20including%2010%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza.%20Another%2017%2C00%2C000%20people%20stand%20displaced.%20Numbers%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this.%20Hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20universities%2C%20homes%2C%20refugee%20shelters%20and%20UN%20offices%20have%20been%20relentlessly%20bombed.%20A%20senior%20UN%20human%20rights%20expert%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F31%2Fun-official-resigns-israel-hamas-war-palestine-new-york%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Gaza%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%20Along%20with%20Gaza%2C%20all%20the%20rules%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20have%20been%20bombed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces.%20Amidst%20this%20destruction%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20for%20liberation%20has%20found%20renewed%20support%20across%20the%20globe.%20Millions%20have%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Berlin%2C%20Paris%2C%20Cairo%2C%20Amman%2C%20Stockholm%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%20Seoul%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%20Wellington%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Islamabad%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Sao%20Paulo%2C%20Bogota%2C%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Santiago%20and%20countless%20other%20cities%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20free%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Israel's%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-hamas-red-herring-evicting-palestinians-gaza%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20New%20York%20has%20witnessed%20protests%20every%20single%20day%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months.%20New%20Yorkers%20of%20all%20colours%2C%20classes%2C%20nationalities%2C%20ethnicities%20and%20religious%20backgrounds%20have%20gathered%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20heart%20of%20the%20American%20empire%20reverberates%20with%20passionate%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9D%20Ceasefire%20now%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20every%20single%20day.%20Subway%20stations%20are%20sprayed%20with%20graffiti%20in%20support%20of%20Gaza.%20People%20wearing%20keffiyeh%20and%20Palestinian%20flags%20in%20solidarity%20have%20become%20a%20common%20sight.%20Poets%2C%20singers%2C%20writers%2C%20actors%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20musicians%2C%20painters%20and%20academics%20are%20all%20lending%20their%20voices%20to%20the%20cause.%20People%20wave%20Palestinian%20flags%20from%20their%20windows%20and%20bus%20drivers%20honk%20loudly%20in%20solidarity%20as%20protesters%20march%20on%20the%20streets.%20Halal%20carts%2C%20run%20mostly%20by%20Arab%20migrants%2C%20are%20witnessing%20longer%20lines%20for%20chicken%20over%20rice%20orders.%20Volunteer-run%20organisations%20from%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20like%20Jewish%20Voices%20for%20Peace%2C%20Palestinian%20Youth%20Movement%2C%20Within%20Our%20Lifetime%2C%20Answer%20Coalition%2C%20Shut%20it%20Down%20and%20many%20others%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20organise%20these%20actions.%20American%20Jews%20have%20participated%20in%20heroic%20civil%20disobedience%20actions%2C%20courting%20arrest%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine.%20Students%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20New%20York%20University%20and%20City%20University%20New%20York%2C%20three%20major%20schools%20in%20the%20city%2C%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20calls%20of%20their%20conscience%20by%20demanding%20that%20their%20university%20leadership%20divest%20from%20Israel.%20Walkouts%2C%20teach-ins%2C%20banner%20drops%20and%20cultural%20gatherings%20have%20been%20organised%20on%20campuses%20to%20break%20the%20uncomfortable%20silences.%20This%20is%20our%20generation%E2%80%99s%20Vietnam%20is%20the%20sentiment%20that%20runs%20across%20the%20American%20student%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123836%2FA7xdsZ0CMAAHgmj.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123836%2FA7xdsZ0CMAAHgmj.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conten