20the%20liberation%20of%20the%20entire%20colonised%20world%2C%20has%20silently%20witnessed%20a%20genocide%20of%20an%20occupied%20and%20colonised%20people.%20India%2C%20a%20country%20that%20gloriously%20fought%20the%20mightiest%20of%20the%20colonial%20empire%2C%20has%20shown%20reticence%20to%20support%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Once%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20a%20newly%20independent%20India%2C%20still%20trying%20to%20stand%20on%20its%20feet%2C%20had%20brought%20the%20agenda%20of%20apartheid%20to%20the%20UN%20tables%20to%20speak%20against%20the%20racial%20violence%20of%20the%20colonisers%20and%20became%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20impose%20sanctions%20on%20apartheid%20South%20Africa.%20A%2075-year-old%20India%2C%20set%20to%20become%20a%20global%20superpower%2C%20has%20not%20found%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20utter%20a%20single%20word%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20even%20at%20a%20time%20when%20fellow%20countries%20in%20South%20America%20and%20Africa%20have%20severed%20their%20diplomatic%20relationships%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Israel%20Ramps%20up%20Military%20Action%2C%20Protective%20Presence%20Activism%20in%20Palestine%20Is%20No%20Longer%20Working%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-israel-ramps-up-military-action-protective-presence-activism-in-palestine-is-no-longer-working%5C%22%3EAs%20Israel%20Ramps%20up%20Military%20Action%2C%20Protective%20Presence%20Activism%20in%20Palestine%20Is%20No%20Longer%20Working%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20social%20media%20users%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Fnews%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-war-conflict-fake-news-disinfo-meghupdates-ajaychauhan41-mrsinha-jix5a-twitter-x-23311%5C%22%3Econtributed%20most%20to%20the%20online%20disinformation%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Israel-Palestine%2C%20demonising%20Palestinians%20as%20terrorists%20and%20sub-humans%2C%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20annihilated%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%20Mainstream%20Indian%20media%2C%20rotten%20for%20many%20years%20now%2C%20has%20acted%20as%20gaslighter%20par%20excellence.%20Comparing%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20situation%20with%20India-Pakistan%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20intellectual%20error%2C%20when%20in%20reality%20it%20is%20the%20pre-independence%20India-British%20empire%20analogy%20at%20play%20here.%20Israel%20is%20a%20settler%20colonial%20formation%20on%20Palestinian%20lands.%20Would%20we%20Indians%20have%20acknowledged%20the%20British%20colonial%20state%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20exist%20over%20India%3F%20If%20the%20answer%20is%20no%2C%20then%20what%20makes%20us%20ally%20with%20Israel%20today%3F%20The%20relentless%20cheering%20and%20valorisation%20of%20Israeli%20military%20actions%20by%20Noida%20media%20in%20the%20name%20of%20war%20reporting%20has%20only%20contributed%20to%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20global%20consent%20of%20this%20genocide.%20Imagine%20someone%20cheering%20General%20Dyer%20during%20the%20Jallianwala%20Bagh%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabid%20islamophobia%20has%20blinded%20our%20moral%20vision.%20Strategic%20deep%20state%20and%20defence%20partnerships%20with%20Israel%20have%20silenced%20our%20fearless%20political%20voices.%20We%20speak%20in%20measured%20tones%2C%20walking%20tight%20diplomatic%20ropes%20on%20this%20issue.%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Eabstention%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20resolution%20speaks%20so%20much%20about%20us%20as%20a%20country.%20In%20strategically%20supporting%20Israel%2C%20we%20have%20ended%20up%20supporting%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20war%20crimes%20known%20to%20man.%20Our%20silence%20on%20Palestine%20has%20muted%20all%20the%20