nt%20who%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20Mr%20Reddy's%20deputy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-to-take-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-who-all-are-invited-4641118%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20To%20Be%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20With%2012%20Ministers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20attended%2C%20as%20did%20party%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20the%20chiefs%20of%20various%20state%20units.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-telangana-chief-minister-congress-revanth-reddy-the-new-telangana-chief-minister-who-had-egg-thrown-at-him-4636632%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevanth%20Reddy%3A%20Next%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Once%20Had%20Egg%20Thrown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Gaddam%20Prasad%20Kumar%2C%20who%20beat%20Anand%20Methuku%20of%20the%20outgoing%20BRS%20and%20trounced%20P%20Naveen%20Kumar%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20win%20the%20Vicarabad%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20will%20be%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWho%20Are%20The%2012%20To%20Take%20Oath%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20the%20incoming%20ministers%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Also%20in%20the%20(short-lived)%20race%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Vikramarka%20is%20a%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20outgoing%20Assembly.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Mala%20community%2C%20listed%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20he%20delivered%2011%20of%2012%20seats%20in%20the%20state's%20Khammam%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20efforts%20for%20the%20Congress'%20win%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20four-month%20padyatra%2C%20or%20foot%20march%2C%20that%20covered%20nearly%201%2C370%20km.%20Mr%20Reddy%20won%20the%20Madhira%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20has%20held%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20third%20Congress%20leader%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20race%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20is%20a%20party%20loyalist%20and%20former%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20to%20boot.%20Now%20a%20seven-time%20election-winner%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20was%20also%20boss%20of%20the%20party's%20state%20unit%20before%20he%20was%20replaced%20with%20Revanth%20Reddy%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20election%20he%20was%20the%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Telangana's%20Nalgonda%20-%20a%20seat%20he%20resigned%20since%20the%20Constitution%20forbids%20an%20individual%20from%20being%20an%20MP%20and%20MLA%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassembly-elections-2023-news-bjp-mps-resign-bjp-mps-who-won-state-polls-quit-as-mps-including-chief-minister-hopefuls-4638603%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20MPs%20Who%20Won%20State%20Polls%20Quit%20Parliament%2C%20Including%20Chief%20Minister%20Hopefuls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20won%20the%20Huzurnagar%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESridhar%20Babu%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Another%20Congress%20loyalist%2C%20Mr%20Babu%20was%20Chairman%20of%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20committee%20and%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20someone%20who%20understands%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20voters.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20community%2C%20he%20was%20also%20a%20MLA%20in%20the%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20(when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power)%20and%20served%20as%20the%20Minister%20for%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20his%20fifth%20term%20as%20a%20MLA%2C%20Mr%20Babu%20won%20the%20Manthani%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20held%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20between%201999%20and%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPonnam%20Prabhakar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20politician%20since%20his%20student%20days%2C%20Mr%20Prabhakar%20is%20the%20former%20Karimnagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%3B%20he%20won%20the%20seat%20-%20previously%20held%20by%20outgoing%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20-%20in%202009%20but%20lost%20it%20to%20the%20BRS'%20BV%20Kumar%20in%202014%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20Goud%20community%2C%20listed%20as%20a%20Backward%20Class%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Husnabad%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKomatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yet%20another%20veteran%20-%20with%20over%20three%20decades%20in%20the%20party%20-%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20another%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20who%20was%20fielded%20in%20this%20election%20and%20who%20has%20resigned%20in%20order%20to%20become%20a%20Telangana%20minister.%20And%2C%20like%20Mr%20Vikramarka%2C%20he%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20Congress%20swept%20his%20district%20-%20the%20party%20won%2011%20of%2012%20seats%20in%20Nalgonda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20won%20the%20Nalgonda%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20won%20thrice%20between%201999%20and%202009%20before%20being%20beaten%20decisively%20by%20the%20BRS'%20KB%20Reddy%20in%202018.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20back%20from%20his%20rival%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDamodar%20Raja%20Narasimha%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20(undivided)%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Narasimha%20was%20also%20Minister%20of%20Higher%20Education%20and%20Agriculture.%20A%20Dalit%20from%20Telangana's%20Medak%20area%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Andole%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20recovering%20it%20from%20the%20BRS%20that%20won%20it%20in%20two%20previous%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPonguleti%20Srinivas%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Elected%20to%20the%20Khammam%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202014%2C%20on%20a%20ticket%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BRS%20in%202018%20and%20the%20Congress%20just%20before%20this%20election.%20Called%20the%20'strongman'%20of%20the%20district%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Palairu%20seat%20by%20over%2056%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDana%20Anasuya%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Popularly%20called%20Seethakka%2C%20Ms%20Anasuya%20is%20a%20member%20of%20a%20tribal%20community%20from%20Mulugu%20district%20and%20is%20fondly%20referred%20to%20by%20incoming%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Bsister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterstingly%2C%20Ms%20Anasuya%20was%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Naxalite%20group%20before%20she%20joined%20politics%3B%20she%20joined%20as%20a%20young%20girl%20but%20quit%20after%20being%20disillusioned%20and%20is%20now%20also%20a%20trained%20lawyer%20with%20a%20Ph.D%20in%20political%20science.%20She%20won%20the%20Mulug%20Assembly%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThummala%20Nageswar%20Rao%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Previously%20with%20ex-Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrabau%20Naidu's%20TDP%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20was%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20with%20that%20party%20before%20he%20joined%20rivals%20BRS%20in%202014%2C%20where%20he%20served%20as%20Minister%20for%20Roads%20and%20Buildings.%20He%20quit%20the%20BRS%20and%20joined%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20this%20election%20because%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Telangana's%20Khammam%20district%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20won%20that%20Assembly%20seat%3B%20he%20earlier%20won%20this%20in%202009%2C%20when%20with%20the%20TDP%20and%20when%20it%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKonda%20Surekha%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20seasoned%20Telangana%20politician%2C%20Ms%20Surekha%20won%20the%20Warangal%20(East)%20Assembly%20seat%20that%20she%20first%20won%20in%20the%202014%2