EThe%20former%20front-office%20employee%20Amit%20Patel%20allegedly%20utilized%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20two%20vehicles%2C%20a%20condominium%2C%20and%20a%20designer%20watch%2C%20among%20various%20other%20items.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20invested%20in%20cryptocurrency%2C%20placed%20bets%20on%20online%20gambling%20sites%2C%20and%20chartered%20personal%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20team's%20name%20was%20not%20disclosed%20in%20the%20federal%20filing%2C%20the%20Jaguars%20have%20affirmed%20that%20Patel%20is%20accused%20of%20embezzling%20from%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaguars'%20Statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20confirm%20that%20in%20February%202023%2C%20the%20team%20terminated%20the%20employment%20of%20the%20individual%20named%20in%20the%20filing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20per%20TheAthletic.com.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20several%20months%20we%20have%20cooperated%20fully%20with%20the%20FBI%20and%20the%20U.S.%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Middle%20District%20of%20Florida%20during%20their%20investigation%20and%20thank%20them%20for%20their%20efforts%20in%20this%20case.%20As%20was%20made%20clear%20in%20the%20charges%2C%20this%20individual%20was%20a%20former%20manager%20of%20financial%20planning%20and%20analysis%20who%20took%20advantage%20of%20his%20trusted%20position%20to%20covertly%20and%20intentionally%20commit%20significant%20fraudulent%20financial%20activity%20at%20the%20team's%20expense%20for%20personal%20benefit.%20This%20individual%20had%20no%20access%20to%20confidential%20football%20strategy%2C%20personnel%20or%20other%20football%20information.%20The%20team%20engaged%20experienced%20law%20and%20accounting%20firms%20to%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20independent%20review%2C%20which%20concluded%20that%20no%20other%20team%20employees%20were%20involved%20in%20or%20aware%20of%20his%20criminal%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheathletic.com%2F5118308%2F2023%2F12%2F06%2Fjacksonville-jaguars-employee-theft-amit-patel%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Athletic%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Efirst%20reported%20the%20news%20earlier%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20information%20from%20team%20media%20guides%2C%20Patel%20served%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20complete%20seasons%20as%20a%20staff%20member%20in%20the%20Jaguars'%20finance%20department%2C%20beginning%20in%202018.%20Prosecutors%20contend%20that%20by%202019%2C%20he%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsole%20administrator%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20organization's%20virtual%20credit%20card%20program%2C%20granting%20him%20the%20authority%20to%20sanction%20new%20accounts%20and%20initiate%20alterations%20to%20the%20available%20credit.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20was%20tasked%20with%20categorizing%20virtual%20credit%20card%20transactions%20in%20business%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20September%202019%20until%20his%20termination%20in%20February%202023%2C%20Patel%20accumulated%20personal%20expenses%20on%20team%20accounts%20by%20fabricating%20certain%20transactions%20and%20exaggerating%2C%20duplicating%2C%20or%20mischaracterizing%20others%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20charging%20documents%2C%20USA%20Today%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20faces%20charges%20of%20wire%20fraud%20and%20engaging%20in%20an%20illicit%20monetary%20transaction%20related%20to%20the%20%2495%2C000%20watch%20he%20bought%20online%20last%20autumn.%20Opting%20to%20be%20charged%20by%20information%20rather%20than%20indictment%2C%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20have%20his%20first%20court%20date%20scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701934500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F56flcivg_amit-patel_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-amit-patel-all-about-indian-american-accused-of-stealing-22-million-from-football-team-4641657%2