Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CGet%20it%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20December%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20nearly%20300%20journalists%20were%20raided%20in%20the%20recent%20case%20involving%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%20argued%20for%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20these%20guidelines.%20She%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Ecopies%20of%20necessary%20data%20on%20devices%20could%20be%20taken%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20seizing%20the%20entire%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Circulates%20Interim%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Devices%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%20of%20the%20matter%20on%20November%207%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20media%20professionals%E2%80%99%20devices%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20matter%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20involved%20confidential%20sources%20and%20their%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20media%20professionals%2C%20they%20will%20have%20on%20their%20phone%E2%80%99s%20sources%2C%20contacts.%20So%2C%20there%20must%20be%20some%20guidelines.%20This%20is%20serious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20Raju%20had%20countered%20this%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20media%20cannot%20be%20above%20the%20law%20and%20there%20may%20be%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20elements%20so%20the%20government%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20%E2%80%9Cshut%20out%20completely%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbalancing%20of%20interests%E2%80%9D%20including%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20balancing%20of%20interests%20and%20better%20guidelines%20need%20to%20be%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20media%20professionals.%20We%20would%20like%20ASG%20to%20work%20on%20this%20and%20come%20back%20on%20this%20issue.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20aspect%20that%20privacy%20is%20held%20to%20be%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20in%20its%20order%20on%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20last%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20had%20circulated%20interim%20guidelines%20for%20seizure%20of%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20by%20five%20renowned%20academics%20%E2%80%93%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20Deepak%20Malghan%20and%20Mukul%20Kesavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20circulated%20draft%20of%20guidelines%20and%20submit%20a%20response%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701932282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftwo-years-on-union-asks-for-another-weeks-time-to-submit-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20petition%20seeking%20framing%20of%2