iminal%20sections%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20and%20Vivo-India%20has%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20apart%20from%20those%20arrested%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20probe%20agency%20arrested%20four%20persons%2C%20including%20the%20MD%20of%20the%20Lava%20International%20mobile%20company%20Hari%20Om%20Rai%2C%20in%20this%20investigation.%20The%20others%20who%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20were%20Chinese%20national%20Guangwen%20alias%20Andrew%20Kuang%2C%20Chartered%20Accountants%20Nitin%20Garg%20and%20Rajan%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20then%20claimed%20in%20its%20remand%20papers%20before%20a%20local%20court%20here%20that%20the%20alleged%20activities%20of%20the%20four%20enabled%20Vivo-India%20to%20make%20wrongful%20gains%20that%20were%20detrimental%20to%20the%20economic%20sovereignty%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20raided%20vivo-India%20and%20its%20linked%20persons%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20busted%20a%20major%20money%20laundering%20racket%20involving%20Chinese%20nationals%20and%20multiple%20Indian%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20then%20alleged%20that%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2062%2C476%20crore%20was%20%26quot%3Billegally%26quot%3B%20transferred%20by%20Vivo-India%20to%20China%20to%20avoid%20payment%20of%20taxes%20in%20India.%20The%20company%20had%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bfirmly%20adheres%20to%20its%20ethical%20principles%20and%20remains%20dedicated%20to%20legal%20compliance.%26quot%3B%20Rai%20had%20recently%20told%20a%20court%20here%20that%20though%20his%20company%20and%20Vivo-India%20were%20in%20talks%20to%20launch%20a%20joint%20venture%20in%20India%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Chinese%20firm%20or%20its%20representatives%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20not%20derived%20any%20monetary%20benefit%2C%20nor%20has%20he%20engaged%20in%20any%20transaction%20with%20Vivo%20or%20any%20entity%20allegedly%20related%20to%20Vivo%2C%20let%20alone%20having%20been%20associated%20with%20any%20alleged%20'proceeds%20of%20crime'%2C%26quot%3B%20Rai's%20lawyer%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20filed%20an%20enforcement%20case%20information%20report%20(ECIR)%2C%20the%20ED%20equivalent%20of%20a%20police%20FIR%2C%20on%20February%203%20after%20studying%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20FIR%20of%20December%20last%20year%20against%20an%20associated%20company%20of%20vivo%2C%20Grand%20Prospect%20International%20Communication%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(GPICPL)%2C%20its%20directors%2C%20shareholders%20and%20some%20others%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Corporate%20Affairs%20Ministry%20alleging%20that%20GPICPL%20and%20its%20shareholders%20used%20%26quot%3Bforged%26quot%3B%20identification%20documents%20and%20%26quot%3Bfalsified%26quot%3B%20addresses%20at%20the%20time%20of%20incorporation%20of%20the%20company%20in%20December%202014.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701930480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Ffq6o12rs_vivo-logo-reuters_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-vivo-money-laundering-case-chargesheet-filed-by-enforcement-directorate-4641436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20filed%20its%20first%20charge%20sheet%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20money%20laundering%20probe%20against%20Chinese%20smartphone%20maker%20vivo%20and%20some%20others%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-