sofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fwill-banks-open-only-for-5-days-a-week-heres-what-you-should-know-about-ibas-proposal%2Farticleshow%2F105802814.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20Army's%20New%20Lens%20For%20Drones%20Can%20Deceive%20Enemy%20Air%20Defence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20has%20developed%20an%20all-weather%2C%20all-terrain%2C%20special%20lens%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20deceive%20the%20enemy%20air%20defence%20systems%20during%20wartime%2C%20helping%20in%20the%20suppression%20and%20destruction%20of%20enemy%20air%20defences%20for%20air%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20conducted%20successful%20trials%20of%20a%20Luneberg%20lens%20which%20is%20attached%20to%20a%20drone%20and%20is%20used%20for%20locating%20enemy%20weapons%20and%20the%20type%20of%20weaponry%20used%20against%20ground%20forces%20and%20aircraft%20and%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Does%20The%20Lens%20Work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Luneberg%20lens%2C%20when%20attached%20to%20a%20drone%2C%20increases%20the%20radar%20signature%20of%20the%20drone%2C%20making%20it%20appear%20like%20a%20helicopter.%20The%20radar%20cross-section%20is%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20target%20to%20reflect%20radar%20signals%20on%20the%20receiver.%20The%20more%20the%20area%20of%20the%20radar%20cross-section%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20target%20is.%20Drones%20have%20a%20small%20radar%20cross-section%20compared%20to%20a%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Luneberg%20lens%20increases%20the%20radar%20signature%20and%20deceives%20the%20enemy's%20air%20defence%20system%2C%20depicting%20the%20drone%20as%20a%20helicopter.%20It%20will%20force%20the%20enemy%20to%20initiate%20air%20defence%20measures%20like%20the%20use%20of%20missiles%20or%20anti-aircraft%20guns.%20%C2%A0The%20lens%20has%20been%20designed%20by%20the%20Army%20Design%20Bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20swarm%20of%20drones%20(multiple%20drones)%20equipped%20with%20the%20lens%20is%20sent%2C%20it%20can%20confuse%20the%20enemy's%20radar%20by%20alerting%20that%20attack%20helicopters%20are%20approaching%20a%20target%20and%20would%20force%20them%20to%20initiate%20air%20defence%20measures%20to%20counter%2C%26quot%3B%20Captain%20Dheeraj%20Umesh%20from%20the%20Army%20Air%20Defence%20(AAD)%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Dheeraj%20Umesh%20from%20the%20511%20Air%20Defence%20Missile%20Regiment%20of%20the%20army%20is%20the%20innovator%20of%20the%20Luneberg%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intelligence%20gathered%20will%20be%20helpful%20for%20future%20operations%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20can%20cover%20a%20360-degree%20area%20on%20the%20radar%20and%20will%20reflect%20radar%20signals%20from%20any%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20help%20the%20force%20locate%20the%20position%20of%20the%20enemy's%20weapon%20and%20the%20type%20of%20system%20deployed%20which%20is%20helpful%20in%20the%20Suppression%20of%20Enemy%20Air%20Defence%20(SEAD)%20and%20Destruction%20of%20Enemy%20Air%20Defence%20(DEAD)%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20can%20be%20used%20to%20conceal%20the%20planned%20route%20of%20heliborne%20operations%20of%20the%20army%2C%20where%20multiple%20quadcopters%20can%20be%20sent%20in%20a%20direction%20deceiving%20the%20enemy%20radar%2C%20making%20it%20a%20suitable%20choice%20of%20aerial%20deception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20lens%20cannot%20depict%20a%20fighter%20aircraft%20but%20the%20officer%20said%20in%20future%2C%20if%20a%20UAV%20or%20a%20drone%20with%20higher%20speed%20is%20developed%2C%20then%20we%20can%20use%20the%20lens%20to%20depict%20a%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll-Weather%2C%20All-Terrain%20Lens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20was%20tested%20in%20March%2C%20where%20the%20OSA-AK%20missile%20was%20fired%20from%20a%20range%20of%206.5%20kilometres%20and%20on%20the%20radar%20system%20in%20an%20Electronic%20Warfare%20Test%20(EWT)%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20has%20a%20range%20of%2015%20kilometres%20and%20can%20fly%20for%2040%20minutes.%20The%20system%20can%20operate%20in%20hot%20deserts%20and%20high-altitude%20mountainous%20terrain.%20The%20production%20cost%20of%20the%20drone%20is%20relatively%20cheap.%20A%20lens%20costs%20around%20Rs%2055%2C000%20and%20the%20cost%20per%20target%20is%20approximately%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20against%20the%20existing%20cost%20of%20Rs%2025-30%20lakh%20per%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701929520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbte4dklg_luneberg-lens-drone_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-armys-new-luneberg-lens-for-drones-can-deceive-enemy-air-defence-4641343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Army%20has%20developed%20an%20all-weather%2C%20all-terrain%2C%20special%20lens%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20deceive%20the%20enemy%20air%20defence%20systems%20during%20wartime%2C%20helping%20in%20the%20suppression%20and%20destruction%20of%20enemy%20air%20defences%20for%20air%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-armys-new-luneberg-lens-for-drones-can-deceive-enemy-air-defence-4641343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-armys-new-luneberg-lens-for-drones-can-deceive-enemy-air-defence-4641343%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-armys-new-luneberg-lens-for-drones-can-deceive-enemy-air-defence-4641343%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20House%20resolution%20urges%20Pakistan%20to%20uphold%20democratic%20institutions%2C%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%22%2C