itional%20cost%20of%20Rs%20840%20per%20month%20for%20vegetarian%20thalis%2C%20and%20Rs%20900%20per%20month%20for%20non-vegetarian%20thalis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fcost-of-home-cooked-vegetarian-meal-rises-by-10-non-vegetarian-thali-by-5-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20version%20of%20Google's%20Gemini%20you%20can%20use%20right%20now%20doesn't%20beat%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AI%20arms%20race%20is%20heating%20up%20between%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571307458e7c0c29a2a8015%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AI%20arms%20race%20is%20heating%20up%20between%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle's%20been%20hyping%20up%20Gemini%20as%20the%20AI%20that%20can%20outperform%20industry%20leader%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20that%20version%20of%20Gemini%20won't%20be%20available%20to%20users%20until%20next%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%2C%20a%20version%20that's%20surpassed%20by%20GPT-4%20is%20available%20on%20Google's%20Bard%20chatbot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-chaos-google-amazon-catch-ai-leader-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20counter%20the%20idea%20that%20it's%20fallen%20behind%20rivals%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20May%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Ftechnology%2Fai%2Fgoogle-io-2023-keynote-sundar-pichai%2F%23ai-products%5C%22%20target%3D