p%3EThe%20New%20South%20Wales%20government%20has%20authorized%20an%20%26quot%3Baerial%20shooting%26quot%3B%20program%20to%20cull%20a%20population%20of%20wild%20horses%20at%20one%20of%20its%20largest%20national%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20culling%20method%20has%20been%20adopted%20as%20part%20of%20a%20state%20mandate%20to%20reduce%20an%20estimated%2017%2C000%20wild%20horses%20in%20Kosciuszko%20National%20Park%20to%20just%203%2C000%20by%202027%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.environment.nsw.gov.au%2Fnews%2Fwild-horse-management-in-kosciuszko-national-park%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficials%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAerial%20shooting%26quot%3B%20would%20involve%20operatives%20firing%20on%20the%20horses%20from%20helicopters%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tactic%20that%20the%20local%20government%20trialed%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20officials%20shot%20270%20horses%20over%20two%20days%20while%20veterinarians%20accompanied%20them%20in%20the%20helicopters%20to%20observe%2C%20the%20New%20South%20Wales%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20veterinarians%20also%20inspected%2043%20of%20the%20horses%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20no%20adverse%20animal%20welfare%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20median%20time%20from%20shooting%20to%20insensibility%20was%205%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20horses%20were%20non-fatally%20wounded%26quot%3B.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20average%20of%207.5%20shots%20were%20used%20to%20kill%20each%20horse%2C%20officials%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20trial%20over%2C%20the%20government%20said%20it's%20moving%20fully%20ahead%20with%20the%20helicopter%20shootings%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20be%20possible%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20the%202027%20deadline%20without%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20government%20estimates%20of%20the%2