re%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20deep%20concerns%20over%20the%20unexpected%20deduction%20of%20%E2%82%B9798.03%20crore%20from%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20IGST%20settlement%2C%20Revenue%20Minister%20Krishna%20Byre%20Gowda%20raised%20significant%20issues%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20government%20has%20adjusted%20the%20IGST%20settlement%20amount%20to%20Karnataka.%20It%20claims%20that%20there%20was%20a%20shortfall%20in%20the%20IGST%20account%20which%20has%20been%20subsequently%20adjusted%20for%20all%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20explanation%20on%20why%20the%20shortfall%20arose%20and%20the%20mechanism%20of%20calculation%3B%20there%20was%20no%20advanced%20notice%20either.%20If%20you%20cut%20Rs%20800%20crore%20in%20a%20month%20from%20us%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20exchange%20of%20information%20or%20proper%20notice%20about%20the%20share%20calculation%20of%20IGST%20and%20the%20reasons%20behind%20it.%20Even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20clarity%2C%20if%20you%20deduct%20Rs%20800%20crore%20without%20any%20notice%2C%20it%20will%20definitely%20affect%20our%20financial%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20website%20of%20GST%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%20%E2%82%B95%2C277.34%20crore%20IGST%20%5Bwas%5D%20collected%20in%20Karnataka%20for%20the%20month%20of%20April%202023%2C%20where%20the%20settlement%20amount%20stands%20at%20%E2%82%B93%2C092.38%20crore.%20In%20the%20following%20month%2C%20May%202023%2C%20%E2%82%B93%2C582.08%20crore%20IGST%20was%20collected%20from%20the%20state%2C%20where%20the%20settlement%20amount%20was%20%E2%82%B92%2C681.87%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20months%20of%20June%2C%20July%