0in%20Cambodia%2C%20where%20she%20has%20another%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20part%20of%20what%20happened%20after%20my%20divorce.%20I%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20live%20and%20travel%20as%20freely.%20I%20will%20move%20when%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Jolie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%2012%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fangelina-jolie-and-brad-pitt-relationship-history-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrad%20Pitt%20and%20Angelina%20Jolie%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20one%20of%20Hollywood's%20most%20iconic%20couples.%20In%202016%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJolie%20filed%20for%20divorce.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20as%20the%20daughter%20of%20two%20actors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjon-voight-slams-daughter-angelina-jolie-palestine-israel-war-stance-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJon%20Voight%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Marcheline%20Bertrand%2C%20Jolie%20added%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bnever%20very%20impressed%20with%20Hollywood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20in%20quite%20a%20shallow%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20all%20the%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Hollywood%20is%20not%20a%20healthy%20place.%20So%20you%20seek%20authenticity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangelina-jolie-hollyood-career-not-actress-move-cambodia-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701922553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657129ac58e7c0c29a2a7ec2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangelina-jolie-hollyood-career-not-actress-move-cambodia-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3BMaleficent%26quot%3B%20star%20says%20that%20she's%20ready%20to%20leave%20Hollywood%20to%20live%20in%20Cambodia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40busines