e.%20And%20for%20another%2C%20they%20managed%20to%20get%20through%20some%20of%20the%20game's%20trickier%20interpersonal%20challenges%20by%20virtue%20of%20the%20bonds%20they%20formed%20with%20other%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223902%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22phill%2C%20mai%2C%20and%20sam%20out%20of%20the%20game%20in%20casual%20party%20wear%20at%20a%20squid%20game%20party%2C%20with%20their%20arms%20around%20each%20other%20and%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570fc5758e7c0c29a2a7aa3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhill%2C%20Mai%2C%20and%20Sam%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20celebration%20in%20Los%20Angeles%3Cp%3EJoe%20Scarnici%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20finalists%20were%20saved%20by%20another%20player%20during%20a%20dormitory%20test%20in%20episodes%20six%20and%20seven%2C%20which%20cut%20the%20player%20count%20down%20from%2031%20to%2020.%20Mai%20was%20the%20first%20picked%2C%20and%20Phill%20and%20Sam%20were%20saved%20by%20other%20plays%20that%20they%20had%20a%20connection%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMai%2C%20however%2C%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20game's%20most%20ruthless%20players%2C%20publicly%20targeting%20Ashley%20(278)%20for%20elimination%20in%20a%20dice%20game%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20her%20lack%20of%20teamwork%20during%20the%20glass%20bridge%20challenge.%20And%20in%20the%20penultimate%20episode's%20circle%20of%20trust%20challenge%2C%20Mai%20targets%20her%20closest%20connection%20%E2%80%94%20and%20successfully%20eliminates%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhill%20is%20the%20MVP%20during%20the%20circle%20of%20trust%20challenge%3A%20Not%20only%20does%20he%20correctly%20guess%20his%20attacker%20twice%2C%20but%20he%20also%20eliminates%20the%20final%20contestant%2C%20Hallie%20Parrott%20(355).%20Sam%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20episodes%2C%20remains%20a%20steady%20presence%2C%20mediating%20Mai's%20conflict%20with%20Ashley%20and%20solidifying%20his%20bond%20with%20Phill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20into%20the%20finale%2C%20Mai's%20actions%20made%20her%20the%20biggest%20wild%20card%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20it%20was%20still%20anyone's%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEventually%2C%20Mai%20took%20home%20the%20final%20prize%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20final%20contestants%20wrap%20things%20up%20with%20a%20formal%20dinner%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20just%20for%20conversation.%20The%20three%20final%20players%20are%20presented%20with%20three%20buttons.%20Pressing%20one%20reveals%20a%20specific%20color%20%E2%80%94%20green%20saves%20the%20player%20and%20allow%20them%20to%20pick%20another%20finalist%20to%20advance%2C%20grey%20has%20no%20effect%2C%20and%20red%20eliminates%20them%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMai%20volunteers%20to%20push%20the%20first%20button%2C%20which%20turns%20grey.%20Sam%20pushes%20the%20next%2C%20revealing%20a%20red%20button%20that%20results%20in%20his%20elimination.%20Phill%20and%20Mai%20mourn%20his%20loss%20and%20hug%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20Mai%20reveals%20in%20a%20confessional%20that%20she%20had%20hoped%20Phill%20would%20be%20her%20final%20opponent%20regardless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20night%20of%20what%20was%20certainly%20fitful%20sleep%2C%20the%20two%20move%20on%20to%20play%20the%20titular%20squid%20game%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20learn%20that%20they'll%20be%20doing%20something%20completely%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20men%20in%20pink%20jumpsuits%20and%20masks%20stand%20under%20spotlights%20next%20to%20a%20squid%20game%20pattern%20on%20the%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570f8720ec98e92f74cf864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20final%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20field%20is%20set%20up%20to%20play%20the%20Korean%20children's%20game%2C%20Phill%20and%20Mai%20learn%20upon%20arrival%20that%20they'll%20instead%20be%20playing%20rock%2C%20paper%2C%20scissors.%20Winning%20a%20round%20of%20the%20game%20allows%20them%20to%20choose%20one%20key%20from%20a%20box%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20it%20opens%20the%20safe%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20field%2C%20they%20win%20the%20entire%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20multiple%20rounds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20plenty%20of%20key%20tries%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Mai%20is%20the%20one%20to%20successfully%20open%20the%20safe%2C%20revealing%20a%20golden%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22phill%20and%20mai%20hug%20on%20squid%20game%20the%20challenge%2C%20wearing%20white%20shirts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571352f0ec98e92f74cffed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhill%20and%20Mai%20hug%20on%20the%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20just%20validates%20that%20anything%20is%20possible.%20Even%20when%20you%20feel%20down%20and%20afraid%2C%20you%20have%20to%20pick%20yourself%20up%2C%20be%20a%20strong%20person%2C%20and%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Mai%20says%20in%20a%20teary%20confessional.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20your%20fear%20is%2C%20fight%20it%20with%20everything%20that%20you've%20got%2C%20and%20you%20can%20accomplish%20anything.%20And%20it's%20proven%20tonight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20ends%20with%20a%20montage%20of%20the%20other%20contestants%2C%20reminding%20us%20that%20even%20after%20losing%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20is%20alive%20and%20well.%20Then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20it%20cuts%20to%20Mai%20inputting%20her%20golden%20card%20into%20an%20ATM%20