the%20company's%20physical%20security%20budget%20by%2050%25%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20or%20around%20the%20evening%20of%20December%201%2C%202022%2C%20Davis%20directed%20Plaintiff%20to%20cut%20the%20physical%20security%20budget%20by%20an%20additional%2050%25%20by%20midnight.%20This%20was%20done%20in%20hours%2C%20not%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosa's%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-davis-boring-company-elon-musk-career-bio-2019-11%23the-boring-companys-chief-executive-slept-at-twitters-headquarters-with-his-partner-and-newborn-baby-following-musk-taking-over-the-social-media-platform-in-late-october-the-information-reported-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavis%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Boring%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20of%20Musk's%20firms%20that%20aims%20to%20build%20tunnel%20networks%20under%20major%20US%20cities%20to%20ease%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exchange%20would%20have%20occurred%20around%20five%20weeks%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Felon-musk-takeover-twitter-controversies-antisemitism-blue-checkmarks-conspiracy-theories-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20took%20over%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20renamed%20X%2C%20on%20October%2028%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20his%20circle%20of%20advisors%20had%20already%20cut%20the%20physical%20budget%20by%2050%25%20during%20that%20period%2C%20meaning%20Davis%20wanted%20it%20slashed%20even%20further%2C%20Rosa's%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20chief%20objected%20to%20the%20decision%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20put%20the%20company%20building%20at%20risk%20of%20violating%20a%20court%20order%20requiring%20Twitter%20to%20safeguard%20user%20data%20and%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building's%20security%20staff%20were%20responsible%20for%20watching%20%26quot%3Bover%20800%20laptops%20and%20other%20electronic%20devices%26quot%3B%20essential%20to%20the%20privacy%20safeguards%2C%20Rosa's%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20being%20told%20to%20cut%20these%20staff%20from%20the%20building%2C%20and%20Rosa%20was%20worried%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20security%20risk%20from%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%20protestors%26quot%3B%20outside%20the%20headquarters%2C%20per%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERosa%20says%20he%20was%20fired%20from%20Twitter%20days%20later%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20raising%20his%20concerns%2C%20Rosa%20received%20a%20call%20from%20Davis%2C%20who%20told%20him%20he%20was%20no%20longer%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20physical%20security%20team%20and%20then%20hung%20up%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20Rosa%20discovered%20he'd%20lost%20his%20company%20access%20and%20was%20effectively%20fired%20without%20an%20official%20explanation%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20also%20alleges%20that%20Davis%20told%20him%20on%20November%2011%2C%202022%20to%20shut%20down%20Salesforce%20at%20Twitter%2C%20which%20the%20company%20used%20to%20share%20information%20with%20law%20enforcement%20about%20%26quot%3Btime-sensitive%20and%20important%20legal%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosa%20disagreed%20with%20the%20decision%2C%20and%20told%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20company's%20legal%20team%20about%20his%20objections%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Rosa%20was%20denied%20his%20promised%20severance%20package%20and%20vested%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20seeks%20compensatory%2C%20emotional%20distress%2C%20and%20punitive%20damages%20from%20Musk%2C%20advisors%20such%20as%20Davis%2C%20and%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosa's%20suit%20is%20one%20of%20several%20already%20filed%20by%20laid-off%20Twitter%20employees%20against%20Musk%20and%20X%2C%20and%20many%20say%20their%20contracts%20were%20breached%20and%20accused%20the%20billionaire%20of%20breaking%20state%20employment%20laws.%3C