C%20who%20weighs%20in%20around%20140%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20the%20whole%20household%20in%20peak%20shape%20starts%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20Ali%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20about%20her%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.everroot.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEverRoot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20dog%20supplement%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20having%20a%20routine%20and%20consistency%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20she's%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20morning%20protein%20shakes.%20Her%20go-to%20recipe%2C%20packed%20with%20flavor%20as%20well%20as%20nutrients%2C%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20scoop%20of%20vanilla%20protein%20powder%20(she%20prefers%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.lailaali.com%2Fcollections%2Fprotein-powders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eown%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20scoop%20of%20collagen%20powder%20for%20healthy%20joints%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20nails%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tablespoon%20of%20almond%20butter%2C%20a%20good%20source%20of%20healthy%20fats%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20splash%20of%20oat%20milk%20for%20texture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dash%20of%20cinnamon%20for%20flavor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20a%20banana%2C%20which%20provides%20carbs%20for%20energy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShe'll%20also%20sometimes%20add%20in%20a%20green%20powder%20for%20even%20more%20nutrients%2C%20as%20well%20as%20whatever%20frozen%20fruit%20is%20on%20hand%20(especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fhealthiest-fruit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-glycemic%20fruits%20like%20berries%3C%2Fa%3E).%20The%20whole%20shake%20is%20blended%20with%20crushed%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20she%20also%20drinks%20plenty%20of%20water%20(aiming%20for%2040%20ounces%20throughout%20the%20morning)%20and%20takes%20a%20daily%20multivitamin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAli%20said%20her%20pets%20are%20'part%20of%20the%20family'%20and%20take%20supplements%20to%20stay%20healthy%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20dogs%20have%20a%20similar%20morning%20routine%3A%20breakfast%2C%20walking%2C%20and%20Everroot%20supplements%2C%20which%20Ali%20said%20are%20easy%20to%20give%20to%20them%20directly%20or%20mixed%20into%20their%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dogs%20also%20get%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-five-hundred-extra-steps-per-day-live-longer-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edaily%20steps%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20by%20following%20Ali%20up%20and%20down%20the%20stairs%20of%20her%20three-story%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20get%20plenty%20of%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20when%20she%20hits%20the%20home%20gym%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20in%20pajamas%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20go%20upstairs%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20want%20to%20come%20back%20downstairs%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20heavy%20bag%20session%2C%20petite%20Malibu%20likes%20to%20tussle%20with%20Buddy%2C%20a%20gentle%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20dogs%20by%20her%20side%20every%20step%20of%20her%20routine%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Ali's%20life%20since%20her%20pro%20boxing%20days%2C%20she%20said.%20Back%20then%2C%20a%20furry%20friend%20would%20accompany%20her%20on%20long%20runs%20while%20she%20trained%20for%20championship%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWherever%20I%20am%2C%20they%20are.%20They're%20part%20of%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboxing-champion-laila-ali-morning-routine-diet-recipe-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701912121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657