This%20Dad%20is%20Making%20it%20Possible%20For%20Parents%20to%20Rent%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%2034-year-old%20Sourabh%20Jain%20first%20became%20a%20father%20to%20his%20daughter%2C%20his%20perspective%20on%20life%20changed.%20Like%20any%20parent%2C%20his%20daughter%20became%20his%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20struggled%20with%20bonding%20with%20her%20in%20the%20beginning.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20so%20tiny%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20speak.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20bond%20with%20her.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298277%2Fnep-early-childhood-care-and-education-play-based-learning-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egames%20and%20books%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20interactive%20and%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20hours%20with%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20began%20the%20hunt%20for%20games%20and%20toys%20that%20not%20only%20helped%20him%20bond%20with%20his%20daughter%20but%20also%20contributed%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59319%2Fharsh-songra-my-child-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20this%20search%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20not%20only%20are%20these%20toys%20and%20games%20hard%20to%20find%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20burn%20a%20hole%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20realisation%20was%20that%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20toys%20eco-friendly.%20There%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20plastic%20always%20present%20and%20it%20is%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20little%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20aspired%20to%20give%20his%20daughter%20the%20world%2C%20he%20also%20endeavoured%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20more%20sustainable%20world%20for%20her.%20Today%2C%20he%20owns%20The%20EleFant%20%E2%80%94%20a%20toy%20rental%20company%2C%20or%20in%20Sourabh%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20labour%20of%20love%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20major%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Indore%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20etc.%20Curious%20about%20how%20the%20business%20works%20and%20how%20you%20can%20rent%20toys%20for%20your%20kids%3F%20Read%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%2C%20age-appropriate%20and%20fun%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Sourabh%20always%20had%20an%20entrepreneurial%20mindset.%20Despite%20working%20as%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20harboured%20a%20persistent%20interest%20in%20starting%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EleFant%20emerged%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20toys%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20brand%20for%20parents%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%